    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim, then finely slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>into wedges</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>chicken stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
