    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> sliced shallot</strong> to the pan with the bacon and reduce the heat to medium, then cook for 1-2 min or until softened</p><p>Add the <strong>chicken stock</strong> and <strong>soft cheese</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to thicken</p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>– this is your<strong> creamy sauce</strong></p>",
